# MIND PALACE 3D TERMS OF USE & END USER LICENSE AGREEMENT (EULA)

Last Updated: 15/01/2025

1. ACCEPTANCE OF TERMS
By downloading, installing, or using the Mind Palace app ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these terms. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not use the App.

2. LICENSE GRANT
We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the App for personal purposes on devices you own or control.

3. SUBSCRIPTION SERVICES
- The App offers subscription-based premium features
- Free tier users have limited access (7 memory points per room, single room access)
- Premium features include unlimited memory points, cloud sync, and multiple room access
- Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the renewal date
- Subscription management and cancellation are handled through your App Store account

4. USER CONTENT
- You retain ownership of your memories and content uploaded to the App
